title: Virgin (2003 film)
text:
Virgin is a 2003 American <a href="drama%20film">drama film</a> directed by <a href="Deborah%20Kampmeier">Deborah Kampmeier</a> and starring <a href="Elisabeth%20Moss">Elisabeth Moss</a>, <a href="Robin%20Wright%20%28actress%29">Robin Wright</a> and <a href="Daphne%20Rubin-Vega">Daphne Rubin-Vega</a>.
Premise.
When teenage Jessie, raised very religiously, finds herself pregnant, with no memory of having had sex, she determines that she is carrying the child of God.
